{"serial": "33032", "department_serial": 29, "code": "ME3081", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "Fluid Mechanics", "ch": "流體力學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chung, Chih-Ang"], "ch": ["鍾志昂"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["2", "3"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "411"}}, {"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["6"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "411"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "機械工程學系", "en": "Department of Mechanical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 41, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "流體力學是機械系的基礎課程，可應用在需多工程領域，這門課旨在瞭解基本的流體動力學現象，進而探討相關工程應用。課程教學目標在幫助學生建立描述與分析流場的概念與能力，以數學和物理方法闡述質量和動量守恆定律，使學生具備探討流體力學相關工程問題的理論基礎，未來可將所學的知識運用於與流體力學相關的工程、環境和生物醫學等領域。", "en": "Fluid mechanics is a fundamental course in the mechanical engineering curriculum, applicable to numerous engineering fields. This course aims to understand the basic phenomena of fluid dynamics and explore related engineering applications. The primary teaching objective is to help students develop the concepts and skills necessary to describe and analyze fluid flow fields. By employing mathematical and physical methods, students will gain a thorough understanding of the principles of mass and momentum conservation. This foundation equips students to address engineering problems related to fluid mechanics and apply their knowledge in fields such as engineering, environmental science, and biomedical engineering studies."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 流體力學簡介與基本概念\n2. 流體靜力學、壓力與浮力之性質\n3. 伯努力方程式及其應用與限制\n4. 流體運動學與雷諾傳輸定理\n5. 質量、動量與能量之控制體積分析\n6. 流體動力學基本微分方程式及其應用\n7. 因次分析\n8. 管流分析，層流與紊流概念", "en": "Chapter 1: Introduction\nChapter 2: Fluid Statics\nChapter 3: Elementary Fluid Dynamics—The Bernoulli Equation\nChapter 4: Fluid Kinematics\nChapter 5: Finite Control Volume Analysis\nChapter 6: Differential Analysis of Fluid Flow\nChapter 7: Dimensional Analysis, Similitude, and Modeling\nChapter 8: Viscous Flow in Pipes"}, "textbook": {"ch": "教科書\nGerhart, A. L., Hochstein, J. I., Gerhart, P. M., 2021, Munson, Young, and Okiishi’s Fundamentals of Fluid Mechanics, 9th Ed., John Wiley ＆ Sons. (滄海書局代理，Tel 04-27088787）\n參考書\n1. Cengel, Y. A. and Cimbala, J. M. 2010, Fluid Mechanics: Fundamentals and Applications, Mc Graw Hill.\n2. Van Dyke, M., An Album of Fluid Motion, Parabolic Press, Stanford, 1982.", "en": "Textbook\nGerhart, A. L., Hochstein, J. I., Gerhart, P. M., 2021, Munson, Young, and Okiishi’s Fundamentals of Fluid Mechanics, 9th Ed., John Wiley ＆ Sons. (滄海書局代理，Tel 04-27088787）\nReference books\n1. Cengel, Y. A. and Cimbala, J. M. 2010, Fluid Mechanics: Fundamentals and Applications, Mc Graw Hill.\n2. Van Dyke, M., An Album of Fluid Motion, Parabolic Press, Stanford, 1982."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席參與 (10％)、作業 (10％)、期中考I (30％)、期中考II (30％)、期末考 (30％)", "en": "Attendance/participation (10％)、homework (10％)、midterm I (30％)、midterm II (30％)、final exam (30％)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二/週五 09:00-10:00 or by appointment", "en": "Tue./Fri. 09:00-10:00 or by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "影片欣賞、專題討論等補充教材", "en": "Supplementary materials"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科", "en": "基礎學科"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知識與技能", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "實驗規劃與資料分析", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "工程設計與整合", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "合作溝通與管理", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理與社會責任", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Engineering Knowledge and Problem Analysis", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "as